column1: This sequence file was used to generate the melody, harmony and bass notes of
my retuning of Chopin's Etude in C (Op. 10, No. 1)
This is pasted in from CSV output of Excel spreadsheet sequencer
I haven't yet figured out how to upload an Excel spreadsheet to GitHub
The column format is as follows:
Voice number  Start time (beats)  Frequency (Hz)  Note Duration (beats)  Loudness (rel. dB)   Stereo position
The base frequency is C = 7040/27 Hz
(The original CSV file starts on the next line)
